songs.title: MØN$73R
songs.lyrics:
Yeah, I feel like a monster
All are stupid, aye
You are my homie
Lil xan are asshole

If you know how I am, you will say "you are too"
You know how I release my fury, aye, I'm very lonely

I just want to be free, I do not want to feel like a monster
Find me if you can, find me if you want
The end is freedom, I think you know what I mean
